			<div><strong>Suevey: What factors would drive you away from the Demogame?</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>I have been following the discussions of the changes that would drive the people away from the demogame.<br />
<br />
From insparation from the thread. I have decided to make an informal survey poll.<br />
<br />
Here are the options for the poll (Most of them are taken from the linked discussion). I have included &quot;Other/Fill in&quot; for people who vote for that option and wish to post there options in this thread.<br />
Variants (OCC, 5CC, etc)<br />
Mods and Addition<br />
Beurocracy<br />
Turnchat Elimination<br />
Making a Two Team DG<br />
Using Vannila Civ<br />
Using C3C<br />
Real Life<br />
Other/fill in<br />
Abstain/I dont like Public Polls<br />
<br />
<a href="http://forums.civfanatics.com/showthread.php?t=109327" target="_blank">Discussion Thread</a><br />
Note: This is a public, multipoll survey. The porpise for this poll is to survey the population of the demogame :).</div>
